name: The Dark David
description: Based on David Statue by Michelangelo, The story of David and Goliath is a biblical one, found in Book 1 Samuel. The teenage David had to defeat the giant Goliath, he could not be defeated by strength since David was smaller. It took cunning and skill to defeat someone bigger than him, and he did so with the slingshot. however, david is a brave figure who quells crime, this is what inspired me, thus making david a superhero like batman
